assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Joyful Honda Co., Ltd., through its subsidiaries, engages in the home improvement retail business in Japan. The company operates home centers, including timber, building materials, paints, tools, hardware, worker essentials, and electrical fittings. It also provides gardening and plumbing supplies, agricultural materials, and machinery repair services. In addition, it provides wallpapers, carpets and curtains, and lighting for redecorating rooms, as well as consumables, and flower, storage goods, stationery and office supplies, drinks and liquor, drugs, outdoor goods, and bicycles. Further, the company operates garden centers, such as flower and vegetable seedlings, plants, compost, fertilizers, plant pots, bricks, paving stones, and other gardening materials. Additionally, it provides pet centers for dogs, cats, animals and birds, as well as pet foods, cages, toys, and trimmer service, and self-service shower facilities. The company also involved in home renovation, art and craft supplies retail, sports club, and maintenance, and tire sales. It operates 17 stores in Ibaraki, Chiba, Saitama, Tochigi, Gunma, and Tokyo, as well as engages in online shopping activities. Joyful Honda Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1975 and is headquartered in Tsuchiura, Japan.
